<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>403 Forbidden</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: sans-serif; 
            text-align: center; 
            padding: 50px; 
            background-color: #f8d7da; /* Merah muda */
            color: #721c24; /* Merah tua */
        }
        .box {
            border: 2px solid #f5c6cb;
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
        }
        h1 { font-size: 50px; margin: 0; }
        .role-badge {
            background: #333; color: #fff; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="box">
        <h1>⛔ 403</h1>
        <h2>AKSES DITOLAK!</h2>
        <p>Maaf <b><%= username %></b>, Anda tidak boleh masuk ke sini.</p>
        <hr>
        <p>
            Role Anda: <span class="role-badge"><%= myRole %></span><br>
            Syarat Masuk: <span class="role-badge"><%= requiredRole %></span>
        </p>
        <br>
        <a href="/dashboard">⬅️ Kabur ke Dashboard</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>